item.title: Why I chose to become a Fashion Designer
item.description: When I was younger, I wanted the attention. I wanted the fame. I. I wanted my name to be the one in the oft’ said sentence of, “did you hear what ___ did?“. The “in crowd”? Without me, they’d just be a crowd…of my fans no doubt. . “I was dreaming of bigger things “Kids were laughing in my classes While I was scheming for the masses…” “Dreaming ‘bout being a big star” “Now I’m smiling from the stage while You were clapping in the nose bleeds” Imagine Dragons, parts of “Thunder”.
